1076
00:52:12,940 --> 00:52:14,846
爸爸 你该提前告诉我们的
Papa, you should have let us know!

1077
00:52:14,847 --> 00:52:15,800
你什么时候到的
When did you get in?

1078
00:52:15,820 --> 00:52:17,880
今天早上  我都忘记有义卖了
This morning. I'd forgotten about the bazaar.

1079
00:52:17,900 --> 00:52:20,840
没有打扰你们劳动真是明智之举
I was right not to distract you all from your labours.

1080
00:52:20,860 --> 00:52:24,086
Harold叔叔的事怎样了
What happened to Uncle Harold?

1081
00:52:24,087 --> 00:52:25,700
他只受了顿训斥
A reprimand, but nothing more.

1082
00:52:25,720 --> 00:52:26,880
看来你没有白白赶过去
So it was worth your going.

1083
00:52:26,900 --> 00:52:29,032
我觉得我没起到什么作用
I don't think I made a bit of difference,

1084
00:52:29,033 --> 00:52:30,800
但就让他们认为我起到了吧
but let's hold on to that fiction.

1085
00:52:30,820 --> 00:52:32,940
- 纽约怎么样   - 很有趣
