1200
00:58:31,460 --> 00:58:34,114
假设你认为有个人涉嫌犯罪
If you thought a man was involved in a crime,

1201
00:58:34,115 --> 00:58:35,340
或是一起事故
or an incident,

1202
00:58:35,360 --> 00:58:37,440
但你不责怪他
but you didn't blame him,

1203
00:58:37,460 --> 00:58:40,520
你甚至觉得正义在他这边
in fact you thought right was on his side,

1204
00:58:40,540 --> 00:58:42,520
你会怎么做
what would you do?

1205
00:58:42,540 --> 00:58:45,440
这个问题稍微理论化了些
It's a bit theoretical for an opinion.

1206
00:58:45,460 --> 00:58:48,520
- 你不认为他是错的吗   - 是的
- But you don't believe he was wrong? -  No.

1207
00:58:48,540 --> 00:58:50,807
看来我所知不多
Well, I'm guessing in the dark,

1208
00:58:50,808 --> 00:58:53,440
但要是我 我会守口如瓶
but...I suspect I would say nothing.

1209
00:58:58,380 --> 00:59:00,540
这不公平 锤子加重了
That isn't fair. It's weighted.

1210
00:59:01,300 --> 00:59:04,400
你来试试吧 Molesley先生 到你了
Go on. You have a go, Mr Molesley.

1211
00:59:04,420 --> 00:59:07,420
不了 如果Jimmy都不成 我更没戏
No, no, I won't manage it if Jimmy can't.

1212
00:59:08,340 --> 00:59:10,460
试试 我想看
Try. I want to see it.

1213
00:59:21,540 --> 00:59:24,400
打得好
Well done!

1214
00:59:25,340 --> 00:59:26,440
你作弊了
That was cheating.

1215
00:59:27,460 --> 00:59:29,540
这个嘛 靠的只是巧劲罢了
Well, it...it's in the arms.

1216
00:59:30,300 --> 00:59:33,540
主要是挥舞 然后就是一点巧劲
It's all to do with the swing, and the swing is in the arms.

1217
00:59:34,300 --> 00:59:36,360
你好啊 Baxter女士
So, Miss Baxter,

1218
00:59:36,380 --> 00:59:39,520
自我走后都发生过什么 说说吧
anything to tell me about life since I've been away?

1219
00:59:39,540 --> 00:59:43,340
没发生什么
No. Nothing's happened.

1220
00:59:46,440 --> 00:59:48,400
如果有事情 我会查出来的
I'll find out if it has, you know.

1221
00:59:48,420 --> 00:59:50,300
离她远点 Barrow先生
Leave her alone, Mr Barrow.

1222
00:59:50,320 --> 00:59:53,400
我们不欢迎海外回来的恶霸
We don't want any bullying brought back from overseas.

1223
00:59:53,420 --> 00:59:55,360
是吧 Baxter夫人
Do we, Miss Baxter?

1224
00:59:55,380 --> 00:59:59,340
现在 你还想看看其它摊位吗
Now, are there any stalls you'd still like to see?

1225
01:00:10,500 --> 01:00:13,500
天哪 终于能在公共场所喝酒了
God, what a relief to be able to drink in public

1226
01:00:13,520 --> 01:00:16,520
再也没有警察突击检查了  去他的禁酒令
without a policeman pouncing. Down with Prohibition.

1227
01:00:16,540 --> 01:00:17,558
这段时间
You can't mean

1228
01:00:17,559 --> 01:00:20,360
你不会是一直都没得喝吧
you never had a drink all the time you were there.

1229
01:00:20,380 --> 01:00:22,440
Harold 自有办法
Harold has his uses.

1230
01:00:22,460 --> 01:00:24,440
我估计也是
I suppose he does.

1231
01:00:24,460 --> 01:00:28,320
希望他两以后别再招惹咱了
And let us hope they both leave us in peace.

1232
01:00:28,340 --> 01:00:30,320
我恐怕这希望不大
A slim hope, I'm afraid.

1233
01:00:30,340 --> 01:00:31,463
Martha想带他来参加
Martha wants to bring him

1234
01:00:31,464 --> 01:00:33,440
明年夏天Rose初次进入社交界的舞会
over next summer for Rose's coming out ball.

1235
01:00:33,460 --> 01:00:34,480
为什么
Why?

1236
01:00:34,500 --> 01:00:35,340
她说她想
She says she wants

1237
01:00:35,341 --> 01:00:38,280
在死前再参加一次伦敦的社交季
to see another London Season before she dies.

1238
01:00:48,340 --> 01:00:51,440
你还在 谢天谢地
You're still here. Thank goodness.

1239
01:00:51,460 --> 01:00:53,954
我提前赶公车 但还是迟了
I caught an early bus, but it was delayed.

1240
01:00:53,955 --> 01:00:55,440
我还以为会错过你
I thought I'd missed you.

1241
01:00:55,460 --> 01:00:57,460
Daisy我正要去车站
I'm off to the station now, Daisy.

1242
01:00:57,480 --> 01:00:59,320
以后也不回来了
And I won't be back.

1243
01:00:59,340 --> 01:01:00,948
我爸爸去世了
My dad's gone and mother's

1244
